directions: Heat olive oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat; saute zucchini until softened, 5 to 10 minutes. Season zucchini with oregano and basil. Add tomato sauce; cook and stir until heated through, about 5 minutes. Sprinkle Parmesan cheese over zucchini mixture.
ingredients: 4 zucchini - peeled, sliced lengthwise, and sliced
title: Zucchini Parmesan with Tomato Sauce
